# Brewfile
# Install with:
#   brew bundle --file=./Brewfile
#
# Notes:
# - `python` tracks the current Homebrew Python 3.
#   If you want a fixed minor version, replace with e.g. `python@3.13`.
# - `docker` (formula) installs the Docker CLI.
# - `docker-desktop` (cask) installs the Docker Desktop app.
# - Mac App Store apps are installed via `mas` in the brew script (not in this file).
#   `mas` requires you to be signed in to the Mac App Store.
# - `gcloud-cli` is a cask. If needed, add:
#     export PATH="$(brew --prefix)/share/google-cloud-sdk/bin:$PATH"

